Package energy.usef.core.model

Model classes for the transport core.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AgrConnectionGroup
    This repository is used to manage AgrConnectionGroup.
    BrpConnectionGroup
    Subclass of ConnectionGroup representing connections grouped with a BRP.
    CongestionPointConnectionGroup
    Subclass of ConnectionGroup representing connections grouped in a Congestion Point.
    Connection
    Connection entity for the planboard.
    ConnectionGroup
    Entity representing a group of Connection.
    ConnectionGroupState
    Join table between ConnectionGroup and Connection.
    Document
    Entity class Document: This class is a base class for documents inside a PtuContainer.
    Exchange
    Entity class Exchange: This class is an implementation for Document classes related to a message.
    FlexOrderSettlement
    Entity carrying information about the settlement of one flex order.
    Message
    Entity class Message: This class is a representation of a Message send or received.
    MessageError
    Entity class MessageError: When a Message is sent an error may occur, this will be stored in this entity.
    PlanboardMessage
    Entity class PlanboardMessage: This class is a representation of a PlanboardMessage.
    PrognosisSequence
    JPA entity to enable a sequence for a PtuPrognosis.
    PtuContainer
    Entity class PtuContainer: This class is a representation of a PTUContainer.
    PtuFlexOffer
    Entity class PtuFlexOffer: This class is a representation of a FlexOffer.
    PtuFlexOrder
    Entity class PtuFlexOrder: This class is a representation of a FlexOrder.
    PtuFlexRequest
    PtuFlexRequest entity class represents the connection on which an aggregator can have a customer.
    PtuPrognosis
    Entity class PtuPrognosis: This class is a representation of a Prognosis.
    PtuSettlement
    Entity exposing the information related the settlement of a flex order for one PTU.
    PtuState
    Entity class PtuState: contains the regime and PTU container state data for a PTU container and a connection group.
    SignedMessageHash
    Entity representing the hash of a incoming signed message.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    AcknowledgementStatus
    An enumeration to represent if a PtuFlexRequest acknowledgement status.
    DispositionAvailableRequested
    Enumeration of the disposition values for a Prognosis.
    DocumentStatus
    Enumeration of the different statuses for a PlanboardMessage entity.
    DocumentType
    An enumeration to represent a document type of PlanboardMessage.
    MessageDirection
    An enumeration to represent if a Message is inbound or outbound.
    MessageType
    An enumeration to represent the type of Message.
    PhaseType
    Enumeration of the different USEF phases.
    PrognosisType
    An enumeration to represent if a PtuPrognosis type.
    PtuContainerState
    An enumeration to represent if a PtuContainer phase type.
    RegimeType
    An enumeration to represent if a PtuContainer regime type.
